data.description: ***This property has an assumable mortgage*** Seller is willing to credit $10k towards roof! Unique Investment Opportunity! Fully-equipped Triplex (three units) conveniently situated near Englewood beaches and downtown area. Enjoy a stunning lakefront view from Unit #6. Some renovation work is required for Unit #5 to maximize rental potential. Unit #4 comes with convenient washer and dryer. All units are equipped with refrigerators and stoves. Unit 4 and Unit 6 are currently leased at $1550 until April 2024, while Unit 5 is on a month-to-month basis at $1200. We welcome inquiries from serious investors only. Prior to scheduling showings, must provide proof of funds or a preapproval letter. Yo hablo espanol!
